"title": "8636: asking",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8636",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The act of making requests of another, as an expression of dependence. Scripture encourages believers to ask things of God in prayer, and gives guidance concerning the motivation in doing so.</p>\n<h2>Asking as an aspect of human relationships</h2>\n<h3>Examples of everyday requests</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh4:20-Josh4:22\">JOS 4:20–4:22</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:10\">ECC 7:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:15\">1PE 3:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:22\">EXO 3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:7\">DEU 32:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:19\">1SA 12:19</a> <em>The people asked for a king</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:3\">2KI 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:1-Neh2:2\">NEH 2:1–2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:10-Dan2:11\">DAN 2:10–2:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:1-Matt2:2\">MAT 2:1–2:2</a> <em>the Magi seek the king of the Jews</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:46\">LUK 2:46</a> <em>Jesus Christ asks questions in the temple</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:9\">JHN 4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:1-Rom16:2\">ROM 16:1–16:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:9-Gal2:10\">GAL 2:9–2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:21\">PHM 1:21</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of stronger appeals</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:2-Phil4:3\">PHP 4:2–4:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen50:17\">GEN 50:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod5:15\">EXO 5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:20\">LUK 23:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts25:3\">ACT 25:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:1\">1TH 4:1</a></p>\n<h2>Asking as an aspect of prayer</h2>\n<h3>General petitions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:7-Matt7:11\">MAT 7:7–7:11</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:9-Luke11:13\">LUK 11:9–11:13</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:6\">PHP 4:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut18:16\">DEU 18:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:39\">JDG 6:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:20\">1SA 1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:4\">1CH 16:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:32-2Chr6:33\">2CH 6:32–6:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:8-Job6:9\">JOB 6:8–6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:3\">PSA 5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:7-Prov30:8\">PRO 30:7–30:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:37-Matt9:38\">MAT 9:37–9:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:1\">1TI 2:1</a></p>\n<h3>Frequent requests for guidance or insight</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam2:1\">2SA 2:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:17\">EPH 1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:21-Gen25:22\">GEN 25:21–25:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:7\">EXO 33:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh9:14\">JOS 9:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:1-1Sam23:2\">1SA 23:1–23:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs8:7-2Kgs8:8\">2KI 8:7–8:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:29-1Chr21:30\">1CH 21:29–21:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:3\">2CH 20:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:2\">ISA 58:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:21\">JER 10:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:9\">COL 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:5\">JAS 1:5</a></p>\n<h2>The grounds for asking</h2>\n<h3>According to God's will</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:14-1John5:15\">1JN 5:14–5:15</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Trusting in God's great mercy</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:18\">DAN 9:18</a></p>\n<h3>In the name of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:13\">JHN 14:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:23-John16:27\">JHN 16:23–16:27</a></p>\n<h3>In faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:22\">MAT 21:22</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:24\">MRK 11:24</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:6\">JAS 1:6</a></strong></p>",
